CONTENTS:

Visual Studio 2010/.NET 4 solution.

Behavior test framework
Behave requirements gathering tool and test editor. 
Supporting utilities for remoting, reports and logging.

LICENSE:
MIT Open Source license. See License.txt for details.


INSTALL BINARIES:
Go to https://github.com/ihenehan/Behavior/tree/master/Build and download Behavior.zip to get the latest build.
Unzip to the folder of your choosing.


Documentation is sparse for now. See the wiki at https://github.com/ihenehan/Behavior/wiki/Behavior-Test-Tools for a little more detail. Once I get the project and build system in order, I'll start putting together better info on the github wiki.

